question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Wat is de locatie van het stadhuis van Gyeongju in Gyeongju, Zuid-Korea?
answer: Het stadhuis van Gyeongju in Gyeongju, Zuid-Korea, bevindt zich aan de 25 Taejong-ro, Gyeongju-si, Gyeongsangbuk-do.
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea, is located at 25 Taejong-ro, Gyeongju-si, Gyeongsangbuk-do.
